               <birth when="1933">He was born at <placeName ref="LOC1071Acafar"/> in <date>1933</date>. </birth>
                  
                  
                  <floruit notBefore="1958" notAfter="1980">He was an important 20th century author. 
                     After he received a traditional education, he joined the modern government school.
                     He then worked as a journalist at the Ministry of Information, beginning in <date>1958/59</date>, 
                     and later an employee at the Ministry of Health, 
                     after which he opted to earn his living by writing. 
                     He became a versatile writer. He published 21 books in Amharic and two in English.
